- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses the semantics of LTL synthesis tools.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as LTL synthesis is a subfield of AI.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the synthesis of reactive systems.
